https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/YUM\" title=\"Yum! Brands, Inc.\">YUM</a></span>) is experiencing the \u2018Fast-Food Exodus\u2019 in an uneven fashion, as evidenced by the recent performance of its brand portfolio. While KFC, Pizza Hut and Habit Burger are struggling</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2189792154/image_2189792154.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747429-yum-brands-taco-bell-eyes-dutch-bros-success", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 11:32:03", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747428", "title": "Moderna: From Breakthrough COVID-19 Vaccines To Personalized Cancer Therapies", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gloved Hand Holding Cancer Vaccine with Syringe on Orange Background\" data-id=\"1284796611\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Cindy Shebley/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Moderna's origins and business overview</h2> <p>Moderna, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MRNA\" title=\"Moderna, Inc.\">MRNA</a></span>), is a biotechnology company focused on developing and commercialising messenger-RNA ((mRNA)) based therapies, targeting a diversity of therapeutic areas including prophylactic vaccines against respiratory infections, personalised cancer therapies, and rare diseases. Moderna</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747428-moderna-stock-from-breakthrough-covid-19-vaccines-to-personalised-cancer-therapies-buy", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 11:29:16", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747432", "title": "EPR Properties: The Big Dividend Yield Is A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image_1414473405.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Topgolf: Golf, Party Venue, Sports Bar &amp; Restaurant, Germantown, MD\" data-id=\"1414473405\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image_1414473405.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image_1414473405.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image_1414473405.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image